{"tid":109493,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"以前有冇玩過MK論壇做版主?","createTime":"2017-02-06T04:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T13:17:50.000Z","uid":30524,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c51e1053ce02d715996a598e64715fa42f71fb1d","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"小六嗰時跟個朋友玩過一個MK論壇，叫眷戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩左年幾申請做版主，之後做埋分版、超版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾FB興起，少左勁多人上論壇<br />\n<br />\n事隔咁多年，啱啱心血來潮上左去睇，最後回覆好似係1月.<br />\n而再上一個回覆已經係12月頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似見證住呢樣野死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec489d4cdea9f8eacb77a012ded8855f1b7511e","tid":109493,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"最高做過貓貓論壇超版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係見證住呢樣野死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503d8eb7405fc4b1d503e969d4ba22fad3f4a5f6","tid":109493,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:04:02.000Z","msg":"有無亂bam人"},{"pid":"99cb14b9c0a5585c4a1cceb9effa46e7a6c36da3","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無亂bam人</blockquote><br />\n冇呀，好守規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰時仲會個個月出版評，寫每個子區版主嘅評語，<br />\n鬧下佢地咁多日唔管版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又試過同論壇吹水POST班熟落D既會員吹水吹到5am<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524d14bf86d86df8ac20fc118a86c14522052b05","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:07:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最高做過貓貓論壇超版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係見證住呢樣野死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個時眷戀d人好想&quot;超貓貓趕5p&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0bc0fff2a14f4ca6a62ec4ed023f1aa6bf8975","tid":109493,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"小眾論壇同出名少少嘅壇都做過版主OR超版<br />\n通常都係ADMIN點名叫我做，我而家都諗唔返起嗰陣做版主到底做過啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e7199bf00c3c291de3c74a5d642012b86eb452","tid":109493,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"做過跑online啲外掛論壇嘅版主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7d4185b1189c33ec6384b21d74517fd77701b9","tid":109493,"uid":31269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:18:09.000Z","msg":"上面咁多位啲論壇版主係咪friend底？會出嚟食飯？<br />\n我以前個壇係會，個壇執左好多年，但當年活躍嘅會員同版主到依家都間唔中約出嚟食飯吹水。"},{"pid":"5efc8ea9f9bf37189895a5266942073ea473a6dd","tid":109493,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:19:28.000Z","msg":"2kf版主<br />\n有同遊戲官方搞過討論區既活動"},{"pid":"d2e18c93a386fae25d6480921b668fada12ed619","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小眾論壇同出名少少嘅壇都做過版主OR超版<br />\n通常都係ADMIN點名叫我做，我而家都諗唔返起嗰陣做版主到底做過啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有apply做, 亦有試過ADMIN點名<br />\n嗰時突然收到admin pm, 受寵若驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做版主到底做過啲乜 &lt;&lt; click click click, 剔D廢POST去回收區, 扣下犯規會員分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d462d4256b74d302fc3290f3f2d2fba86b723d22","tid":109493,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面咁多位啲論壇版主係咪friend底？會出嚟食飯？<br />\n我以前個壇係會，個壇執左好多年，但當年活躍嘅會員同版主到依家都間唔中約出嚟食飯吹水。</blockquote><br />\n有約但果陣太毒一直都唔敢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11eeb5b9a66a3b673aed5967f703cbd242fe108e","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面咁多位啲論壇版主係咪friend底？會出嚟食飯？<br />\n我以前個壇係會，個壇執左好多年，但當年活躍嘅會員同版主到依家都間唔中約出嚟食飯吹水。</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我玩嗰個係幾小圈子<br />\n熟嘅先可能會出<br />\n以我所知 個論壇可能約20個版主, 當中版主A同版主B見過兼好FD<br />\n版主C同版主D都見過<br />\n係得呢4個<br />\n<br />\n當年活躍嘅版主係MSN有個大Group吹水,<br />\n後尾除左fb興起, wtsapp都興起, MSN冇乜人上, 就冇再聯絡<br />\n<br />\n其實好多版主心態係覺得自己高會員一等咁, 所以都係版主同版主玩, 會員同會員玩, 而d會員又好想同版主玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437742c4d4483f5d671b1509163ce4f8be3c8107","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上面咁多位啲論壇版主係咪friend底？會出嚟食飯？<br />\n我以前個壇係會，個壇執左好多年，但當年活躍嘅會員同版主到依家都間唔中約出嚟食飯吹水。</blockquote><br />\n有約但果陣太毒一直都唔敢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到自貼區個撚個都mk得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我完全冇諗過出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131ca4581262a280a1674930a6e96d716a14e617","tid":109493,"uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:31:26.000Z","msg":"做過hkcc 唔記得咩版版主"},{"pid":"0aa94aa73919719d597eca5c791be7186adfe31b","tid":109493,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"你所講嘅野 好快會再係高登發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a43e8c8e4e468cb041f12f28ba3af3c4ab34859","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你所講嘅野 好快會再係高登發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔撚係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b07f608553dba3cc1ff0337d9b5e88bf93c58b","tid":109493,"uid":54871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56b10f009aca34c83ec703662c63b6f94d890afc","tid":109493,"uid":5372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:40:39.000Z","msg":"岩岩上左你果個眷戀睇<br />\n在線會員<br />\n- 201 人在線<br />\n<br />\n都有200上線..真定假架呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0541c4567ac2598f574e0f7514f594d98d56fef4","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:42:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩上左你果個眷戀睇<br />\n在線會員<br />\n- 201 人在線<br />\n<br />\n都有200上線..真定假架呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下 我開呢個post前一秒上，一人在線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5efafb0141dc45c53769dca36c86db2711007bc","tid":109493,"uid":31269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩上左你果個眷戀睇<br />\n在線會員<br />\n- 201 人在線<br />\n<br />\n都有200上線..真定假架呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自動+200<br />\n即係得你一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc4a6f4e2a200179124ec317e1cee3a2d2a6e53","tid":109493,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"會員自貼區超版<br />\n成日私下pm女會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1695956885740e5da9b57eb835c8b921ec2dde7","tid":109493,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ccbe8fea16939b956ddedf31527f00f47c50b75","tid":109493,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9cc21e27d6d2c2d714f30a5a10ad48858c9d1897","tid":109493,"uid":31269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上面咁多位啲論壇版主係咪friend底？會出嚟食飯？<br />\n我以前個壇係會，個壇執左好多年，但當年活躍嘅會員同版主到依家都間唔中約出嚟食飯吹水。</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我玩嗰個係幾小圈子<br />\n熟嘅先可能會出<br />\n以我所知 個論壇可能約20個版主, 當中版主A同版主B見過兼好FD<br />\n版主C同版主D都見過<br />\n係得呢4個<br />\n<br />\n當年活躍嘅版主係MSN有個大Group吹水,<br />\n後尾除左fb興起, wtsapp都興起, MSN冇乜人上, 就冇再聯絡<br />\n<br />\n其實好多版主心態係覺得自己高會員一等咁, 所以都係版主同版主玩, 會員同會員玩, 而d會員又好想同版主玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做版主點都有啲虛榮心，但做耐左又覺得無咩特別。<br />\n個壇當年某啲活躍會員，你俾版主佢都唔肯做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae0c71d9082f006549f615cf5e28ddbb396baea","tid":109493,"uid":15140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:46:56.000Z","msg":"做過樂古版主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e809cf9e8a6bfa6f0646b352f1833d494fcce97f","tid":109493,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:48:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03ff60db391be3265ac408556ccc8e3bf6668c8e","tid":109493,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33ba5e7e0888d9d79ce25a0fa0554a7ac64fdffb","tid":109493,"uid":31712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"我都有上眷戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有材之素屋"},{"pid":"ec079394aa72c7766d7ff4cc06682645b140e412","tid":109493,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會員自貼區超版<br />\n成日私下pm女會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇食過囡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲唔講啦"},{"pid":"99a863a10fe4ab167a7d3e2600bf901c9d8cc3ad","tid":109493,"uid":38765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"以前勁鐘意上眷戀<br />\n次次上都揀唔同theme轉<br />\n因為個個都好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前喺第個細啲嘅論壇做過版主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n申請左勁耐先做到<br />\n一成功左覺得自己好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家諗返真係好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前一放學返屋企就係上論壇<br />\n一上可以上勁耐"},{"pid":"92dd2b9b622720b3f1ff2576bef18b734431ead1","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上面咁多位啲論壇版主係咪friend底？會出嚟食飯？<br />\n我以前個壇係會，個壇執左好多年，但當年活躍嘅會員同版主到依家都間唔中約出嚟食飯吹水。</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我玩嗰個係幾小圈子<br />\n熟嘅先可能會出<br />\n以我所知 個論壇可能約20個版主, 當中版主A同版主B見過兼好FD<br />\n版主C同版主D都見過<br />\n係得呢4個<br />\n<br />\n當年活躍嘅版主係MSN有個大Group吹水,<br />\n後尾除左fb興起, wtsapp都興起, MSN冇乜人上, 就冇再聯絡<br />\n<br />\n其實好多版主心態係覺得自己高會員一等咁, 所以都係版主同版主玩, 會員同會員玩, 而d會員又好想同版主玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做版主點都有啲虛榮心，但做耐左又覺得無咩特別。<br />\n個壇當年某啲活躍會員，你俾版主佢都唔肯做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">免費幫人打工，錢又唔係分俾你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真, 而且做小版主嗰時, 管少一兩日都比超版喺版評度點名話你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我做左超版之後都咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e3172e3774258f77e1055b9e8796c95fa2687a","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:51:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前勁鐘意上眷戀<br />\n次次上都揀唔同theme轉<br />\n因為個個都好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前喺第個細啲嘅論壇做過版主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n申請左勁耐先做到<br />\n一成功左覺得自己好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家諗返真係好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以前一放學返屋企就係上論壇<br />\n一上可以上勁耐</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係呀!!!!!"},{"pid":"529e74ccb245b07687915ca6d273f882c419da13","tid":109493,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2kf版主<br />\n有同遊戲官方搞過討論區既活動</blockquote><br />\nbtw<br />\n2kf版主當年買野可以r discount"},{"pid":"2be072a55316f194a6abcc24aa78dc14d682e880","tid":109493,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"就係你班仆街亂鳩咁bam我ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44517ecafdf89fc71d66ee44e5da29d912b111f0","tid":109493,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3be92d4d81a79087eeb591f53ff1700a12f03b2f","tid":109493,"uid":38765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:55:55.000Z","msg":"以前仲好興申請banner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你俾啲圖同埋想點設計比嗰個人<br />\n嗰個人就會幫你整<br />\nPhotoshop仲未話好興嗰時<br />\n仲有人用photoimpact整<br />\n要填嗰啲表格申請<br />\n同埋要用論壇嗰啲錢俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f758d8291cdbfacff2a9600a1a6a52a8e5cc6af5","tid":109493,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislik