玩，有5千蚊題目，再落左1萬蚊，5萬咁，又有3個錦囊)<br />\n後期玩到背熟哂佢個pool d題目，次次都贏哂1百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲都有玩呢個壇？"},{"pid":"028d22c67bf9772576fecfe0637141944c0f222b","tid":109493,"uid":77797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:09:14.000Z","msg":"做過漫遊嘅版主，當時一啲色情野都無。記得有期跌人流跌得幾勁，同上面傾話不如加個成人版嚟加吓人流，上面堅決反對，話唔想搞色情野。<br />\n結果依家變咗援交網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f09c5a843816f5f34636883629bf9b4b6ffd6a","tid":109493,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小眾論壇同出名少少嘅壇都做過版主OR超版<br />\n通常都係ADMIN點名叫我做，我而家都諗唔返起嗰陣做版主到底做過啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有apply做, 亦有試過ADMIN點名<br />\n嗰時突然收到admin pm, 受寵若驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做版主到底做過啲乜 &lt;&lt; click click click, 剔D廢POST去回收區, 扣下犯規會員分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好似乜撚都冇做過，日日如常水照吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a93d2cd5642f094da5c195922558fdd7b4c6ed6","tid":109493,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:33:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c918d1150ea1397f74afefc7395a3b0268f40491","tid":109493,"uid":8935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:33:58.000Z","msg":"2000fun 版主<br />\n同過GC搞活動"},{"pid":"c1247cd3f59df2987c2ba009df68cf46c514acce","tid":109493,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:36:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1263dd2f6273ce7e407e13f0d32d120cf0376a5d","tid":109493,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:45:17.000Z","msg":"以前我係kyo 版主 仲推左個版主 去做超版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk